- enter zip code and click search to retrieve a list of restaurants in the zip code
- this uses google's places api to retrieve information
- scrolling to the bottom triggers fetch of more data as made available by api
- long clicking/holding the cell will cause it to save ot the favorites list 
  (saved into shared preferences so that it will persist across life cycle changes)


